sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Application
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant CFWebhook as CodeFlare Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant RayController as RayCluster Controller
    participant AppWrapperCtrl as AppWrapper Controller
    participant KueueAPI as Kueue API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayDashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTPS mTLS

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation and Security Enhancement

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI->>CFWebhook: Mutating webhook call<br/>mTLS client cert
    CFWebhook->>CFWebhook: Inject OAuth proxy<br/>Add mTLS config
    CFWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Modified RayCluster spec
    K8sAPI->>RayController: RayCluster event
    RayController->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth Service<br/>Create Secrets (CA, OAuth)<br/>Create Route/Ingress<br/>Create NetworkPolicies
    RayController->>RayController: Generate CA cert<br/>for mTLS
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster created

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 2: AppWrapper Workload Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: Create AppWrapper<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>CFWebhook: Validating webhook call<br/>mTLS
    CFWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation passed
    K8sAPI->>AppWrapperCtrl: AppWrapper event
    AppWrapperCtrl->>KueueAPI: Create Kueue Workload<br/>Bearer Token
    KueueAPI-->>AppWrapperCtrl: Workload admitted<br/>(when resources available)
    AppWrapperCtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy wrapped resources<br/>atomically
    K8sAPI-->>User: AppWrapper admitted

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 3: Ray Dashboard Access (OpenShift with OAuth)

    User->>Route: Access Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ (edge)
    Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ (reencrypt)
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Check OAuth session
    alt Not authenticated
        OAuthProxy->>User: Redirect to OpenShift OAuth
        User->>OAuthProxy: OAuth callback<br/>with auth token
    end
    OAuthProxy->>RayDashboard: Forward authenticated request<br/>HTTPS/8265 mTLS (client cert)
    RayDashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard response
    OAuthProxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Ray Dashboard UI

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 4: Certificate Generation and Rotation

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over CFWebhook: cert-controller manages webhook certs
        activate CFWebhook
        CFWebhook->>K8sAPI: Update webhook-server-cert Secret
        deactivate CFWebhook
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over RayController: Operator generates Ray cluster CA certs
        activate RayController
        RayController->>RayController: Generate CA cert/key
        RayController->>K8sAPI: Create {raycluster}-ca-secret
        deactivate RayController
    end
